Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:14.93,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.14,0:00:15.27,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.83,0:00:18.91,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.49,0:00:23.03,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.03,0:00:26.79,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:30.45,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.45,0:00:34.10,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.10,0:00:36.84,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.77,0:00:40.30,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.39,0:00:45.06,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.06,0:00:48.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.69,0:00:51.20,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.31,0:00:54.98,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.90,0:00:59.54,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.54,0:01:03.19,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.49,0:01:11.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:13.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.44,0:01:15.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.30,0:01:18.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:23.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker high commander Doctor\NDeath formulates a plan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.35,0:01:29.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,to erupt all the world's volcanoes\Nsimultaneously at the dawn of the new year.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.45,0:01:32.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He plans to run his first\Ntest in Kyushu, Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.94,0:01:37.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,On advice from the first Kamen\NRider, Hongo Takeshi, in Europe,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.74,0:01:41.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,the second Kamen Rider, Ichimonji\NHayato, has headed for Kyushu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:44.59,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Doctor Shinigami sent the\Nmighty Snowman after them,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.59,0:01:47.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,but the Rider team of Takeshi and\NHayato put an end to Snowman for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.24,0:01:52.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Shocker wasn't finished\Nwith the volcanoes of Kyushu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:58.20,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs155\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,190.389)}Magma Monster Ghoster
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:58.20,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx90\fs125\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(507.167,660.389)}The Great Battle of Sakurajima
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.75,0:02:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing out of the ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.69,0:02:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.\NLet's search this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.21,0:02:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.45,0:02:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.22,0:02:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I need bigger eruptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.62,0:02:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Call Ghoster!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.93,0:02:21.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Shocker cyborg known as\NGhostar is a terrifying monster
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.13,0:02:25.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,that can move freely in temperatures\Nas high as 5000 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.47,0:02:29.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker seeks to use this\Nheat-resistant monster
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.20,0:02:31.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,to control the flow of magma.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.45,0:02:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- Be careful.\N- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.15,0:02:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... this earthquake\Nis really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:03:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Something really is going\Non in this volcanic region.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.25,0:03:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.25,0:03:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghoster.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you completed the tunnel between\NSakurajima and the Ebino Highlands?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.86,0:03:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too hot in there.\NThe workmen can't take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.27,0:03:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're running out of\Nhumans, just find some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.41,0:03:26.56,Italics,,0,0,0,,This is the Earthquake\NMonitoring Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:29.51,Italics,,0,0,0,,There's a high chance of an\Neruption in Sulfur Valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.59,0:03:33.90,Italics,,0,0,0,,There's a high chance of an\Neruption in Sulfur Valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:37.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,Attention, hotel residents.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:39.15,Italics,,0,0,0,,This is the Earthquake\NMonitoring Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:42.28,Italics,,0,0,0,,There's a high chance of an\Neruption in Sulfur Valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:45.59,Italics,,0,0,0,,Hotel residents,\Nplease board the bus at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.59,0:03:47.68,Italics,,0,0,0,,This is an extremely\Ndangerous situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.68,0:03:49.34,Italics,,0,0,0,,Please board the bus at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.34,0:03:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:52.38,Italics,,0,0,0,,This is the Earthquake\NMonitoring Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.38,0:03:55.30,Italics,,0,0,0,,There's a high chance of an\Neruption in Sulfur Valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.30,0:03:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.33,0:03:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.60,0:04:00.17,Italics,,0,0,0,,Please board the bus at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.19,0:04:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Take us with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mom!\N- Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop this bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let us on!\N- Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.05,0:04:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let us on!\N- Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.74,0:04:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.85,0:04:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet they're with Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. I gotta let Hayato know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.29,0:04:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You wait here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.30,0:04:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, let that child on board!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! We have no use for\Nchildren or the elderly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.37,0:04:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. What are you\Nplanning to do with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.85,0:04:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Shocker errand boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.37,0:04:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.21,0:04:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Foolish humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,From this day forth,\Nyou serve the great Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, take me back to my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.83,0:05:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You monster... darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.02,0:05:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill all who oppose me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- I can't go on.\N- Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is too awful...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.47,0:05:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- Tatsuji...\N- Hang in there, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hang in there,\Nand I'm sure help will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Increase our speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Take us to Shocker's\Nunderground tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.48,0:05:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.94,0:05:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.03,0:05:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.50,0:05:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where Mom went...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, son?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.23,0:05:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Got a stomachache?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A man shouldn't sulk like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They took my mom away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.25,0:06:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you tell us just\Nwhat happened, son?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.05,0:06:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where he went off to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn. It sounds like\Nsomething Shocker would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.81,0:06:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't stop you,\Nbut only one of us needs to pursue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how do we decide?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.56,0:06:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You or me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.45,0:06:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.22,0:06:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to get me with\Na double-headed coin, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.53,0:06:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.91,0:06:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Heads!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take the boy home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.05,0:07:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Where should we meet up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.10,0:07:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say the overlook\Non Sakurajima.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.81,0:07:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.12,0:07:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.51,0:07:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll contact Taki and Pops\Ntoo, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.42,0:07:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.64,0:07:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.27,0:07:32.58,Italics,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji, nothing personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:36.68,Italics,,0,0,0,,But both sides of\Nthe coin were tails.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hurry up!\N- Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.66,0:07:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Get walking!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.41,0:07:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep walking!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop lagging behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.55,0:08:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... what have you\Nbrought us here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to dig us\Na tunnel to Sakurajima.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- What?\N- But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.06,0:08:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, let me go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.18,0:08:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.19,0:08:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A suspicious figure\Nis approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.09,0:08:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.31,0:08:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker must have a base nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.71,0:08:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.68,0:08:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He came all the way\Nfrom Switzerland...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.61,0:08:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Blow him away with\Nthe land mines!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.57,0:08:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.45,0:09:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.99,0:09:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me to your base, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.21,0:09:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I'll never tell!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.47,0:09:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.57,0:09:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider... die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.21,0:09:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, Armadillong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.09,0:10:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.37,0:10:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Shocker's\Nnewest monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Ghoster!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider... try me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.18,0:10:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,On my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.69,0:11:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Rider Kick\Nwon't work on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... that's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold my power to endure\Nup to 5000 degrees!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.99,0:11:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.32,0:11:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even my cyborg body would\Nlast one minute down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.71,0:12:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Too hot for you, Kamen Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.17,0:12:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:21.51,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(311,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.38,0:12:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a use for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.04,0:12:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider was originally\Na cyborg created by Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.11,0:12:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet he prattles on about justice,\Npeace, and love for his fellow man...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.63,0:12:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Such absolute nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Those made by Shocker\Nmust serve Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:13:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold... the power of the mind\Ncontrol device I've attached to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we can control\Nhim subconsciously.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you mean to make the first\Nand second Kamen Riders...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.86,0:13:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let traitor fight traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:33.87,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H17146E&\3c&HAD7B00&\fs70}Sakurajima
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.88,0:13:40.38,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\c&H188385&\3c&H736C4D&}Sakurajima
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.44,0:13:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where\NHayato got off to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.59,0:13:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd he even come\Nto Sakurajima for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.18,0:13:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hopeless, Hayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.96,0:13:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.78,0:13:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.31,0:13:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.89,0:14:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There's another\Ntelescope over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That one's out of order.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for\Nsomeone important!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.26,0:14:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So am I! Don't hog it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.51,0:14:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You jerk! You'll pay for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.42,0:14:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- Take this, you jerk!\N- Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.96,0:14:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.78,0:14:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Say uncle, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.93,0:14:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You stupid little...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.66,0:14:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.82,0:14:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- You jerk!\N- Dang it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.98,0:14:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.92,0:14:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if it isn't Goro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.13,0:14:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's all this fighting about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.32,0:14:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Goro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.05,0:14:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuji here is looking\Nfor his lost mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! You were the kid who\Nwas crying in front of the hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.01,0:14:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I remember you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are Pops and Taki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.57,0:14:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They were taken by Shocker,\Nalong with Tatsuji's mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:14:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.57,0:14:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.94,0:15:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They were all taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.59,0:15:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I could use this to\Nget in touch with Taki...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.02,0:15:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ichimonji Hayato.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.61,0:15:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you wish to save your allies,\Ncome to the island's caldera.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.67,0:15:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The island's caldera?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.67,0:15:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Ichimonji Hayato,\Naccept Shocker's invitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.14,0:15:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go, Hayato! It's a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.87,0:15:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There are times when, for the greater\Njustice, a man must walk into a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll understand\Nwhen you're older.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.71,0:15:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsuji,\NI will save your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.69,0:15:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you, wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.72,0:15:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.94,0:15:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Work! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.90,0:16:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Stop slacking off!\N- Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.11,0:16:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hurry up!\N- Stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.04,0:16:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- Get up!\N- Don't touch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.79,0:16:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.87,0:16:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Don't do it, Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.17,0:16:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hang in there\Nuntil Hayato comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.39,0:16:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got you.\NDon't give up hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.62,0:16:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker! Death!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.62,0:16:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come, just as promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.42,0:16:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo! You had me worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.44,0:16:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You both betrayed Shocker...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, let the traitor\Nkill the traitor!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.90,0:17:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker is controlling\Nyour mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.21,0:17:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.76,0:17:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.86,0:17:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo, it's me!\NDon't you recognize me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.22,0:17:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.51,0:18:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo... regain your senses!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.11,0:18:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Switch over your brainwaves!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.52,0:18:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost there...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.80,0:18:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's down to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.78,0:18:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.85,0:19:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.34,0:19:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.09,0:19:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that didn't go\Nthe way you hoped...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even thousands of kilometers\Napart, we're linked by telepathy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.25,0:19:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I used that to restore Hongo\Nback to his right mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.13,0:19:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, try us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.54,0:19:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your plan now, Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.73,0:20:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.61,0:20:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you take the\Npeople you kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.35,0:20:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.51,0:20:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all in the tunnel...\Nwhere they're about to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:20:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.02,0:21:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about to explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.56,0:21:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo, let's go save the people!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.71,0:21:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,To the underground tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.79,0:21:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.70,0:21:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Took you long enough, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.98,0:21:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, get the people outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.42,0:21:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- What about you?\N- I'm going to find Death!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, everyone!\NGet out of here! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.30,0:21:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hongo.\N- Ichimonji?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.02,0:21:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Death?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.95,0:21:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like he's\Nabandoned this base.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.46,0:21:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Any luck in the tunnel?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.88,0:21:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all out safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.03,0:21:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's join them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.73,0:22:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to speak to\NMr. Tachibana and Taki again...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.57,0:22:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But it would be harder\Nto leave Japan if I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.23,0:22:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I belong in Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.94,0:22:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Remain well, all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.46,0:22:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The other man who fights\Nevil, Hongo Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.81,0:22:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.48,0:22:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the true hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.03,0:23:10.59,Cont,,0,60,140,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.99,0:23:14.03,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.99,0:23:14.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.74,0:23:16.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the monstrous Fly Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.49,0:23:19.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The capsules dispersed by the\Nfly-robots that Fly Man controls
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.99,0:23:23.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,makes the members of the Tachibana\NRacing Club try to kill Ichimonji Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.34,0:23:25.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider is in peril!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.13,0:23:26.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week\Nfor more Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.46,0:23:29.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "The Demonic Assassin,\Nthe Eerie Fly Man!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.65,0:23:30.99,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs125\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(467.167,220.389)}The Demonic Assassin
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.65,0:23:30.99,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs155\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(507.167,640.389)}the Eerie Fly Man
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.93,0:23:40.77,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.35,0:23:43.35,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.35,0:23:45.31,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.31,0:23:48.36,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.86,0:23:50.73,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.73,0:23:52.61,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.61,0:23:54.40,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.40,0:23:55.85,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.29,0:23:58.24,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.29,0:24:04.01,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.01,0:24:07.54,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.54,0:24:11.22,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.59,0:24:15.29,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Magma Monster Ghoster\NThe Great Battle of Sakurajima
Comment: 0,0:23:26.65,0:23:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The Demonic Assassin,\Nthe Eerie Fly Man!